shuffle(int) - Method in class cscd211Game.Classes.Deck
The shuffle method random shuffles the cards the number of times of the int passed in This must be done as random and generic as possible, meaning if a new Suit or Value is added to the enumerated type you will not need to update this method.
Suit - Enum in cscd211Enums
Simple Suit enumerated type - A Suit is comprised of CLUBS, DIAMONDS, HEARTS, SPADES in that specific order A Suit contains private data members of a String for the suit name and an int for the rank.
Suit(int, String) - Constructor for enum cscd211Enums.Suit
The private explicit value constructor.
suit - Variable in class cscd211Game.Classes.Card
The reference to the enumerated type for the Suit
